column16: Elvis Andrus lines into a double play, third baseman Travis Shaw to first baseman Hanley Ramirez.   Rougned Odor doubled off 1st.
Rougned Odor singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Jackie Bradley Jr.
Ryan Rua walks.   Ian Desmond to 3rd.    Nomar Mazara to 2nd.
Adrian Beltre lines out to center fielder Jackie Bradley Jr.
Nomar Mazara walks.   Ian Desmond to 2nd.
Ian Desmond singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Jackie Bradley Jr.
Shin-Soo Choo flies out to right fielder Mookie Betts.
Mitch Moreland grounds into a force out, second baseman Dustin Pedroia to shortstop Xander Bogaerts.   Adrian Beltre scores.    Ryan Rua to 3rd.    Elvis Andrus out at 2nd.    Mitch Moreland to 1st.
Curt Casali out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher William Cuevas to second baseman Dustin Pedroia.   Kevin Kiermaier to 3rd.
Kevin Kiermaier doubles (3) on a soft line drive to right fielder Mookie Betts.
Tim Beckham pops out to third baseman Travis Shaw in foul territory.
Steven Souza Jr.   doubles (2) on a fly ball to left fielder Brock Holt.   Desmond Jennings scores.
Desmond Jennings grounds into a force out, first baseman Hanley Ramirez to shortstop Xander Bogaerts.   Steve Pearce out at 2nd.    Desmond Jennings to 1st.
Evan Longoria flies out to left fielder Brock Holt.
Brandon Guyer singles on a line drive to left fielder Brock Holt.  Brandon Guyer out at 2nd, left fielder Brock Holt to second baseman Dustin Pedroia.
Curt Casali pops out softly to first baseman Hanley Ramirez.
Kevin Kiermaier pops out to catcher Christian Vazquez in foul territory.
